   version stable 20100323
   require bzip2 gzip
  optional libgcrypt '' '' to use libgcrypt instead of openssl to generate sha1sum
  optional openssl   '' '' to use openssl instead of libgcrypt to generate sha1sum
  category archive
 attribute console
    source ftp://ftp.berlios.de/pub/sdelta/files/sdelta3-$VERSION.tar.bz2
      info home http://sdelta.berlios.de
      desc 'dictionary compressor
sdelta3 primary use is to reduce
the amount of bytes transferred
when source upgrades are downloaded.
It can reduce the average downloading amount
for upgrading source tarballs better than 90%

sdelta3 must be installed and the sdelta
feature enabled within sorcery for
Sorcerer boxes to request and download
source upgrade patches.'

build(){
make &&
make install PREFIX=$DESTDIR/usr &&
sed -i  '/xz\*/a\        XZ*) echo "xz"    ;;' $DESTDIR/usr/bin/sd3
}

current(){
 case $VERSION in
  20100323) grep -q XZ /usr/bin/sd3 ;;
 esac
}
